\newlabel{fig:sigma_ell_boundary}{{9}{8}{Mean improvement ratio (global KL / ISR KL) across the sigma--ell grid. All non-degenerate cells ($\ell \ge 0.50$) exceed 1}{figure.caption.62}{}}
